'''鏟齒象科'''（[[學名|學名]]：Amebelodontidae）為[[長鼻目|長鼻目]]下一個已滅絕的科，是現存[[象|象]]的近親，屬於大型[[草食性|草食性]][[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]。鏟齒象科的物種原先被分類至[[嵌齒象科|嵌齒象科]]下，最近的研究才將牠們重新分類至獨立的科別<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=Shi-Qi |last2=Deng |first2=Tao |last3=Ye |first3=Jie |last4=He |first4=Wen |last5=Chen |first5=Shan-Qin |date=5 January 2016 |title=Morphological and ecological diversity of Amebelodontidae (Proboscidea, Mammalia) revealed by a Miocene fossil accumulation of an upper-tuskless proboscidean |url= |journal=Journal of Systematic Palaeontology |edition=Online |doi=10.1080/14772019.2016.1208687 |pages=1–15}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mothé|first1=D |last2=Ferretti|first2=MP|last3=Avilla|first3=LS|date=12 January 2016|title=The Dance of Tusks: Rediscovery of Lower Incisors in the Pan-American Proboscidean ''Cuvieronius hyodon'' Revises Incisor Evolution in Elephantimorpha| journal=PLoS ONE |doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0147009|pmc=4710528 |pmid=26756209 |volume=11 |page=e0147009}}</ref>。

==食性==
在過去，鏟齒象科物種外型類似鏟子的下顎被認為用來於水中鏟起[[水生植被|水生植被]]。然而，透過研究格氏鏟齒象（''P. grangeri''）與巴氏鏟齒象（''P. barnumbrowni''）下顎獠牙的磨損形式後，科學家認為牠們其實是棲息於[[疏林草原|疏林草原]]的物種，透過下顎獠牙來剝取樹皮或是切斷植物<ref>Lambert, David (1992) "The feeding habits of the shovel-tusked gomphotheres: Evidence from tusk wear patterns" ''Paleobiology 18.2'' https://www.jstor.org/stable/pdfplus/2400995.pdf Retrieved October 2012</ref>。

